Title: EVIL EYE Collection Journal Vegan Leather Notebook
Description:
White Vegan Leather Hardcover / Gold Foil Stamped Cover / 120 GSM Clear Ivory Sheets with Gold foiling edges / Elastic Fastener / Silk Bookmark Ribbon / Back Cover Envelope / A5 Size

These Journals came to life from a personal need of me always looking for a notebook or paper and pen to have in hand to put down ideas, a sentence I heard that touched my soul, or write down a memory I just witnessed.. A lot of amazing moments happen in life that just vanish after 5 minutes from our brains, and I love to keep them forever with me. If you really think and want to keep your memories alive you, me and all of us do have 5 minute every 4 hours to learn the Art of Writing. I also made sure to make the journals look like a book so it can be passed down to your loved ones, children .. etc - with whomever one day you might decide to share your personal life story.

Title: Pomegranate Amulet of Life
Description:
Charged during the Waxing moon for Love, Fertility and Abundance also by bringing Harmony into ones Family Home.

At weddings in Western Armenia (any woman in any religion can do the ritual) , a bride would throw a pomegranate and break it into pieces. Its scattered seeds ensured that the bride would bear children. In Van, Armenian women who wanted to have a son would eat bread made from dough mixed with pomegranate seeds.

“Three pomegranates fell down from heaven: One for the story teller, one for the listener, and one for the whole world.”
